name: Touchy Tezzard
description:
Tezzard #3156 escaped captivity and got lost in the jungles of Honduras, only to stumble upon the Lost City of the Monkey God, where it practiced meditation with the Methodical Monkeys and achieved ultimate enlightenment, thus experiencing the very energetic essence of the cosmos. Still a bit touchy, though.

A trippy tribute to Tezzardz #3156 by Omgidrawedit.
